name: Gradient Cat
description: The NFT image showcases a white Cat perched atop a colorful gradient background. The Cat's eyes are hidden behind a pair of gradient-colored glasses, giving the feline a stylish and mysterious appearance. The Cat's fur is soft and fluffy, and its body is relaxed and at ease. The gradient background adds a sense of vibrancy and energy to the image, complementing the Cat's cool demeanor. Overall, the NFT image is a playful and fashionable take on the classic image of a Cat, making it a unique addition to any digital art collection.
